{
  "stem": "1292.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was like [NON-ENGLISH], which was like saying half a story, right?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she opened the window and pulled me by the hands to try to give me the stamp for my husband.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in this instant when I was inside there was [NON-ENGLISH], I think, was the man, the Gestapo man who was-- and he was in trouble because there was a great pressure on him to give-- not to give so many stamps, right?",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, he came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was very distressed, and the last thing I remember he hit me very hard over the head because I was wrongly placed there at the time, you know?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He hit me over the head, and I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I did fell unconscious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I can't tell you how long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I only know when I did wake up I was very dizzy, and I remember I did have the [NON-ENGLISH] for my husband with a stamp and I saved him from going.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I must have been there for quite some time because when I come to, there wasn't many people there anymore, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was nobody there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I just made my way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So this [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And what happened to you after?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometime, you know, when my-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For some-- sometime when I have a pressure in my head, which I sometime have, you know, when I don't feel so good, I always think maybe because of what happened to me then.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that's-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] gradually the ghetto supposed to be liquidated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember it was several transport.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They arrive and I see them walking the whole families, brave people not knowing what with their little packets or whatever they did think they need to take.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
